Zindagi bhi kitni ajeeb h n ,
qismat ka likha chaahe kitna hi karwa ho ,
hm sb sahhh lete h or aage badhte jaate h , 
pr kch faisle kuch waqt aise hote h jinko dil nhi manna chahta h , 

dil chahta h ki bs ye waqt theher jaaye bs kuch der or ye faisle thamm jaaye, 
ye woh waqt h jb hamein pta hota h ki jiske sath abhi h wo shyd kuch saalo baad nhi hoga , 
or ye khayal aate hi dil sehem jaata h. 

Ye woh aik insan h jisko dekh kr dil ki dhadkan to nhi badhti
pr yahi wo h jisko dekh kr *hi* sirf dil dhadakna chahta h ,
saansein apna surrr badalne lgti h , 
chahre pr aik muskurahat hoti h, halki pr bht gahri hazaro ehsaas ko chupaye rhti h .

Ye wo insaan h jisko paane ki ziddd nhi hoti h bs uske aaspaas hone se ya uske khayal se hi dil aik khushbu se bharrrne lgti h...

Aisa insaan sbki zindagi me koi aik to hoga n ?

 
Jo apna n ho kr bhi apno jaisa ehsaas karaye , 
jisse khoon ka rishta n ho pr ye rishta 
khoon se zyada gahre rang bharrde zindagi me .

Aisa rishta jiska koi naam n ho ,
aisa rishta jisme ehsaas bayan krne ko lafzo ki zarurat n ho,
Aisa jo har muskurahat ka mausam smjhe ,
Aisa jo har hansi ka raaz jaane,
Aisa jo aaiyne se zyada saaf ho, 
Aisa jo aankho ko pdhle 
Aisa jo aankho se baatein kre
Aisa rishta jo mohtaaj n ho kisi waade ka.
Aisa insaan jo sirf aapke liye soche,
Aisa insaan jiski hr dua me aakhri naam sirf aapka ho,
Andhere se darr lge to aapke liye wo apni raatein khuli aankho me guzaarde ,
Jo aapki neendo me bhi aapke sath ho aik dhundli tasweer bn kr,
Jiski palke bheeg jaaye aapke maathe ki shakan dekh kr

Jo waqt aane pr aapke liye saans Lena bhi chorde
Jo aapke liye sb kch krke bhi apne liye kch n mange.

Han wahi jo shyd abhi aapke khayalo me aik muskurahat liye aaya h ðŸ¥¹

Agar aapke paas h koi aisa to use jaane matt dena , 
ye dunya cheenegi tmse pr tm use thaame rkhna tm use khona mtttt ,
kyunki jb umr dhalne lgegi , jb chahre ki taazgi madham ho jayegi ,
jb honth ki nami khtm ho jayegi,  

Tb aik shaam tmhare dil ke kisi kone se aik halki muskurahat liye yahi insaan aayega or tmhare dil ko wahi purani khushbu se bharr dega,, 
pr ye ehsaas bht kamzor hogi , 
Aankhein khulte hi ye manzar kahi gayab sa ho jayega ye khushbu doobne lgegi jaise suraj doob jaata h.
Ye wo waqt hoga jb tm aankhein kholne se darrrne lgoge , 
dunya ki karwahat or un rishto ki Haqeeqat jaan chuke hoge jiske liye tmne is anjani si Khushi or aik narm raushni ko kho diya tha jo sirf Aaj dil ki gahraiyo me bs bujhte diye ki trh aakhri baar jagmagane lgi h ,

jo aaj pata nhi Kahan se aakar tmhe bechain kr gya h ,
shyd aik umr ke baad log isi wajah se so nhi paate 
shyd isliye hi log bs aankhein bnd kiye din guzaarte h ,
shyd wo apni khushbu ko talaash krte rhte h shyd wo aakhri narm raushni ko mahsoos krte rhte h 
Shyd wo darrrte h aankh kholne se, 
shyd wo apna sb kch de kr bs us aik khushbu ko mahsoos Krna chahte h jise barso phle dunya ki is shor me kho diya tha .

Pr aaj afsos ke siwa kch n baaki rhega 
Aaj zindagi me sbse zyada bebasi mahsoos hogi 
Jb wo khusbu door jaane lgegi dil se hamesha ke liye 
Jb wo narm raushni dil ko garm rkhna chorne lgegi 

Or shyd isi waqt is dunya ko alvida Krna chahta h dil

Shyd isi wajah se marrte waqt jism thndi prne lgti h....ðŸ¥º

